       set_altitude         SetAltitudeAction
       toggle_engine        ToggleActuatorAction
       toggle_camera        ToggleActuatorAction
       take_picture         TakePictureAction

 /red_wasp/fly              MoveToAction
           set_altitude     SetAltitudeAction
           toggle_engine    ToggleActuatorAction
           toggle_beacon    ToggleActuatorAction

 /blue_wasp/fly
            set_altitude    SetAltitudeAction
